text:
A post shared by Eiza (@eizagonzalez) on Feb 10, 2018 at 1:44pm PST

Do blondes have more fun? Eiza Gonzalez will soon find out!

The Baby Driver star dramatically changed her look in just one sitting, but it’s all for an upcoming project.

“I’m coming for ya only @colorbymattrez can make me from dark brown to platinum blonde in one day for a movie and keeping my hair healthy,” she captioned the boomerang on her Instagram.

She later gave us a better look and her new blond locks by with another photo while sporting a blue halter top.

Most recently, the Mexican beauty starred in Justin Timberlake’s “Supplies” music video.
title: Eiza Gonzalez Switches Up Her Look and Goes Blonde
